# The AI Tramp Freighter

[Tramp Freighter Blues](https://github.com/Ovid/tramp-freighter/) is a game that I wrote entirely with AI. I did not read the code. I did not review the code. After months of work, I felt I was finally at the point where I could build larger AI systems using only English as my programming language. It's roughly 30,000 lines of React and TypeScript. I don't know React or TypeScript.

